706076f-a.title: Brooklyn: Portland Avenue N. - Park Avenue
706076f-a.text:
North Portland Avenue, west side, between Park and
Flushing A9enues, looking north from near the former and
showing a W. P. A. sewer project. The houses bear No's.
44 to 32.
July, 1935
Works Progress Administration
Five Boroughs Project
CREDIT LINE IMPERATIVE
